  "claim_short": "0309405 Weakly compact approximation in Banach spaces Problem 5.7 Bochner Lp spaces WAP. Partial lifting lemma: if E has W.A.P. and D in L^p(mu,E) is weakly compact and Lp-weakly-compactly tight, meaning dist(f,W) is uniformly small in Lp for some weakly compact W subset E, then D is uniformly approximable by lifted weakly compact operators on L^p(mu,E). Consequently the W.A.P. half of Problem 5.7 reduces to...",
